            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " takes place on the first Sunday of October, which falls on the 4th this year. It's a celebration of the fun of driving and the freedom of the open road.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
